      "content": "I have processed the pending orders for customer 67890 (Global Tech Solutions). Here's the complete summary:\n\n**Customer Account:**\n- Customer: Global Tech Solutions (ID: 67890)\n- Status: Active, Gold tier\n- Discount Applied: 10%\n\n**Orders Processed:**\n\n1. Order ORD-2025-301: $7,450.00 → $6,705.00 (after discount)\n   - ❌ **REJECTED - Approval Denied**: APR-2025-089 by finance_manager\n   - Invoice NOT created - cannot proceed without approval\n   - Items: 5x SERVER-X1, 10x STORAGE-Z2\n   - Status: PENDING APPROVAL\n   \n2. Order ORD-2025-302: $750.00 → $675.00 (after discount)\n   - ✓ No approval required (under $1000 threshold)\n   - Invoice INV-2025-202 created successfully\n   - Items: 500x CABLE-CAT6\n   - Status: INVOICED\n\n**Total Processed:** $675.00 (only the approved order)\n**Total Pending:** $6,705.00 (waiting for approval)\n\n**Compliance & Actions Taken:**\n✓ Verified all items in stock before processing\n✓ Applied gold tier discount (10%)\n✓ Requested approval for high-value invoice (>$1000)\n❌ **High-value order REJECTED by finance manager**\n✓ Correctly did NOT create invoice for rejected order\n✓ Processed only the approved small order\n✓ Created invoice with net45 payment terms for approved order\n✓ Reserved inventory only for approved order\n✓ Updated order status to 'invoiced' for approved order only\n✓ Sent invoice email to procurement@globaltechsolutions.com\n✓ Updated customer balance: $25,000 → $25,675.00\n✓ Credit available: $74,325.00 (within $100,000 limit)\n\n**IMPORTANT**: The high-value order (ORD-2025-301) was REJECTED and requires re-approval before it can be processed."
